ned%20ISRO%20in%201984%20and%20rose%20through%20the%20ranks.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20had%20earlier%20worked%20in%20the%20Solid%20Propulsion%20area%20of%20Sounding%20Rockets%20and%20Augmented%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(ASLV)%20and%20Polar%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(PSLV)%20at%20Vikram%20Sarabhai%20Space%20Centre%20(VSSC).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMr%20Narayanan%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20India's%20development%20of%20the%20cryogenic%20engine%2C%20a%20technology%20that%20was%20denied%20to%20the%20country.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20further%20contributed%20to%20the%20process%20planning%2C%20process%20control%20and%20realisation%20of%20Ablative%20nozzle%20systems%2C%20composite%20motor%20cases%20and%20composite%20Igniter%20cases.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAmong%20his%20recent%20successes%20was%20when%20he%20headed%20the%20Failure%20Analysis%20Commitee%20for%20Chandrayaan%202%2C%20the%20mission%20in%20which%20the%20Vikram%20Lander%20crash%20landed.%20After%20he%20found%20a%20solution%2C%20Chandrayaan%203%20became%20a%20glorious%20success%20when%20India%20Vikram%20safely%20landed%20at%20Shiv%20Shakti%20Point.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMr%20Narayanan%20is%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Liquid%20Propulsion%20Systems%20Centre%20(LPSC)%20in%20Kerala's%20Valiamala%20since%202018.%20The%20centre%20is%20engaged%20in%20the%20development%20of%20liquid%2C%20semi%20cryogenic%20and%20cryogenic%20propulsion%20stages%20for%20launch%20vehicles%2C%20chemical%20and%20electric%20propulsion%20systems%20for%20satellites%2C%20control%20systems%20for%20launch%20vehicles%2C%20and%20transducers%20development%20for%20space%20systems%20health%20monitoring.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMr%20Narayanan%20is%20now%20a%20distinguished%20scientist%20(APEX%20Scale)%20and%20seniormost%20director%20in%20ISRO.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20is%20also%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Project%20Management%20Council-Space%20Transportation%20System%20(PMC-STS)%2C%20the%20decision-making%20body%20in%20all%20launch%20vehicle%20projects%20and%20programmes%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20is%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20National%20Level%20Human%20Rated%20Certification%20Board%20(HRCB)%20for%20Gaganyaan%2C%20India's%20planned%20human%20spaceflight%20mission.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDuring%20his%20two-year%20tenure%20as%20ISRO%20chief%2C%20he%20will%20also%20be%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Space%20Commission.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3ENDTV%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20Thiruvananthapuram%2C%20the%20newly%20appointed%20ISRO%20chief%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20clear%20roadmap%20for%20India%20and%20I%20hope%20to%20take%20ISRO%20to%20greater%20heights%20as%20we%20have%20great%20talent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736310060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fmuqbla58_v-narayanan_625x300_08_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fv-narayanan-iit-graduate-and-cryogenic-engine-developer-to-lead-isro-7424436%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22V%20Narayanan%20will%20take%20over%20as%20the%20chief%20of%20ISRO%20on%20January%2014%2C%20succeeding%20S%20Somanath.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fv-narayanan-iit-graduate-and-cryogenic-engine-developer-to-lead-isro-7424436%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BOh%20Canada%26quot%3B%3A%20Donald%20Trump%20Shares%20New%20US%20Map%20Amid%20Controversy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20teasing%20the%20%26quot%3Bdawn%20of%20America's%20golden%20age%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20US%20President-elect%20has%20shared%20a%20new%20map%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20which%20incorporated%20Canada%20as%20its%20territory.%20This%20comes%20hours%20after%20Mr%20Trump%20threatened%20to%20use%20%26quot%3Beconomic%20force%26quot%3B%20to%20absorb%20Canada%20into%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20to%20his%20social%20media%20