%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhoever%20kidnaps%20or%20abducts%20any%20woman%20with%20intent%20that%20she%20may%20be%20compelled%2C%20or%20knowing%20it%20to%20be%20likely%20that%20she%20will%20be%20compelled%2C%20to%20marry%20any%20person%20against%20her%20will%2C%20or%20in%20order%20that%20she%20may%20be%20forced%20or%20seduced%20to%20illicit%20intercourse%2C%20or%20knowing%20it%20to%20be%20likely%20that%20she%20will%20be%20forced%20or%20seduced%20to%20illicit%20intercourse%2C%20shall%20be%20punished%20with%20imprisonment%20of%20either%20description%20for%20a%20term%20which%20may%20extend%20to%20ten%20years%2C%20and%20shall%20also%20be%20liable%20to%20fine%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20law%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20whoever%2C%20by%20means%20of%20criminal%20intimidation%20as%20defined%20in%20this%20Sanhita%20or%20of%20abuse%20of%20authority%20or%20any%20other%20method%20of%20compulsion%2C%20induces%20any%20woman%20to%20go%20from%20any%20place%20with%20intent%20that%20she%20may%20be%2C%20or%20knowing%20that%20it%20is%20likely%20that%20she%20will%20be%2C%20forced%20or%20seduced%20to%20illicit%20intercourse%20with%20another%20person%20shall%20also%20be%20punishable%20as%20aforesaid%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20issued%20yesterday%2C%20Hardoi%20police%20said%20the%20woman%20visited%20the%20police%20station%20after%20the%20FIR%20was%20registered.%20%26quot%3BRajeshwari%20said%20her%20husband%20Raju%20would%20abuse%20her%20and%20beat%20her%20up.%20Upset%20with%20this%2C%20she%20went%20to%20her%20relative's%20home%20in%20Farrukhabad.%20The%20allegations%20that%20the%20woman%20left%20with%20someone%20are%20false%20and%20baseless.%20We%20are%20taking%20further%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736308680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fqk52u3a8_harpalpur_625x300_07_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-up-woman-did-not-