ivision%20Blizzard%20had%20some%2010%2C000%20employees%20as%20of%202022%2C%20but%20Microsoft%20has%20enacted%20mass%20layoffs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere's%20the%20history%20of%20the%20company%20behind%20iconic%20games%20like%20Call%20of%20Duty%20and%20World%20of%20Warcraft.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EActivision%20Blizzard%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20well%20known%20publishers%20in%20the%20video%20game%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeadquartered%20in%20Santa%20Monica%2C%20California%2C%20the%20company%20is%20best%20recognized%20for%20its%20popular%20franchises%2C%20including%20Call%20of%20Duty%2C%20Diablo%2C%20Overwatch%2C%20World%20of%20Warcraft%2C%20and%20Candy%20Crush%20Saga.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EActivision%20Blizzard%20made%20major%20international%20headlines%20following%20complaints%20about%20working%20conditions%20and%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-set-to-buy-activision-blizzard-billion-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft's%20%2469%20billion%20acquisition%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023.%20The%20all-cash%20deal%20saw%20shareholders%20of%20Activision%20receive%20a%20buyout%20of%20%2495%20per%20share.%20Following%20the%20purchase%2C%20Microsoft%20reported%20revenue%20from%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-xbox%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EXbox%3C%2Fa%3E%20division%20increased%2061%25%20by%20January%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20everything%20to%20know%20about%20the%20creation%20of%20Activision%20Blizzard%2C%20its%20successes%2C%20and%20the%20many%20controversies%20that%20have%20dogged%20the%20company%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2296b64624-98da-416c-840f-3235d08ac92e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20merger%20that%20created%20Activision%20Blizzard%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EActivision%20Blizzard%20was%20formed%20in%202008%20through%20the%20merger%20of%20Activision%20and%20Vivdeni%20Games.%20The%20Activision%20name%20dates%20back%20to%2