%20going%20to%20be%20changing%20the%20name%20of%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%20to%20the%20Gulf%20of%20America.%20What%20a%20beautiful%20name.%20And%20it's%20appropriate.%20It's%20appropriate.%20And%20Mexico%20has%20to%20stop%20allowing%20millions%20of%20people%20to%20pour%20into%20our%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPANAMA%20CANAL%2C%20GREENLAND%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20he%20won%20the%20Nov.%205%20election%20Trump%20has%20talked%20about%20the%20U.S.%20buying%20the%20Danish%20territory%20of%20Greenland%2C%20and%20the%20U.S.%20retaking%20control%20of%20the%20Panama%20Canal.%20He%20declined%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20rule%20out%20military%20or%20economic%20action%20as%20part%20of%20those%20desires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20say%20this%2C%20we%20need%20them%20for%20economic%20security.%26quot%3B%20Trump%20did%20not%20commit%20to%20negotiating%20a%20treaty%20with%20Panama%2C%20but%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BLook%2C%20the%20Panama%20Canal%20is%20vital%20to%20our%20country.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20being%20operated%20by%20China%2C%20China%2C%20and%20we%20gave%20the%20Panama%20Canal%20to%20Panama.%20We%20didn't%20give%20it%20to%20China%2C%20and%20they've%20abused%20it.%20They've%20abused%20that%20gift.%20It%20should%20have%20never%20been%20made.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EELON%20MUSK%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%2C%20the%20Tesla%20chief%20executive%20and%20Trump's%20choice%20to%20co-chair%20a%20commission%20aimed%20at%20cutting%20government%20spending%2C%20has%20criticized%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20Sir%20Keir%20Starmer%20in%20recent%20days%20over%20his%20performance%20when%20Starmer%20was%20the%20UK's%20director%20of%20public%20prosecutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20said%20Starmer%20failed%20to%20prosecute%20gangs%20of%20men%20who%20raped%20young%20girls.%20Starmer%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20Musk%20knew%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20nothing%26quot%3B%20about