ent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatch%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fisro-s-new-rocket-soorya-at-93-metres-taller-than-qutab-minar-840093%5C%22%3EScientist%20V%20Narayanan%20Speaks%20To%20NDTV%20About%20ISRO's%20'Soorya'%20Rocket%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Narayanan%20is%20a%20distinguished%20scientist%20(APEX%20Scale)%20and%20seniormost%20director%20in%20ISRO.%20The%20Liquid%20Propulsion%20Systems%20Centre%2C%20which%20he%20heads%2C%20is%20engaged%20in%20the%20development%20of%20liquid%2C%20semi-cryogenic%20and%20cryogenic%20propulsion%20stages%20for%20launch%20vehicles%2C%20chemical%20and%20electric%20propulsion%20systems%20for%20satellites%2C%20control%20systems%20for%20launch%20vehicles%2C%20and%20transducers%20development%20for%20space%20systems%20health%20monitoring.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20also%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Project%20Management%20Council-Space%20Transportation%20System%20(PMC-STS)%2C%20the%20decision-making%20body%20in%20all%20launch%20vehicle%20projects%20and%20programmes%2C%20and%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20National%20Level%20Human%20Rated%20Certification%20Board%20(HRCB)%20for%20Gaganyaan%2C%20India's%20planned%20human%20spaceflight%20mission.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20studied%20in%20Tamil-medium%20schools%2C%20Mr%20Narayanan%20chief%20completed%20his%20M%20Tech%20in%20Cryogenic%20Engineering%20and%20PhD%20in%20Aerospace%20Engineering%20from%20IIT%2C%20Kharagpur%2C%20where%20he%20was%20awarded%20a%20Silver%20Medal%20for%20achieving%20the%20first%20rank%20in%20the%20M%20Tech%20programme.%20The%20rocket%20and%20spacecraft%20propulsion%20expert%20joined%20ISRO%20in%201984%20and%20rose%20through%20the%20ranks%20to%20become%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Liquid%20Propulsion%20Systems%20Centre%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%20Somanath%20took%20over%20as%20the%20ISRO%20chief%20in%20January%202022%20and%20it%20was%20under%20him%20that%20India%20bec