y%20would%20pursue%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeagler%20added%20that%20self-driving%20rideshare%20vehicles%20are%20such%20a%20new%20and%20developing%20field%20that%20there%20is%20no%20set%20standard%20for%20personal%20injury%20yet.%20Moreover%2C%20he%20said%20that%20a%20malfunction%20would%20have%20to%20substantially%20impair%20the%20vehicle's%20operation%20to%20rise%20to%20the%20level%20of%20negligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohns%20said%20by%20publicizing%20his%20experience%2C%20he%20isn't%20looking%20to%20stop%20Waymos%20from%20accepting%20passengers%2C%20but%20he%20does%20want%20the%20company%20to%20be%20more%20transparent%20about%20these%20types%20of%20malfunctions%20and%20the%20technology's%20limitations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Waymo%20terms%20of%20service%20do%20not%2C%20at%20the%20time%20of%20publication%2C%20warn%20of%20potential%20vehicle%20malfunctions%20or%20any%20risks%20of%20using%20the%20driverless%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20new%20world%20that%20we've%20never%20known%20before%20and%20autonomous%20vehicles%20are%20ushering%20in%20a%20new%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20Johns%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I'm%20super%20all%20for%20it%2C%20but%20the%20big%20thing%20that%20we%20have%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20we're%20all%20a%20part%20of%20the%20experiment%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we're%20paying%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20experiment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmalfunctioning-waymo-trapped-passenger-inside-drove-in-circles-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736290403000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677c8a9dd741e3aee2a14742%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmalfunctioning-waymo-trapped-passenger-inside-drove-in-circles-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Los%20Angeles%20man%20was%20stuck%20in%20a%20Waymo%20vehicle%