.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fced8qw8q62jo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fced8qw8q62jo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20School%20Friends%20Turned%20Entrepreneurs%20Are%20Helping%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Farmers%20Earn%20Profits%20With%20%E2%80%98Foreka%E2%80%99%20Oils%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELow%20wages%20and%20the%20relentless%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363341%2Fdelhi-police-constable-amit-lathia-teaches-underprivileged-low-income-children-for-competitive-exam-helps-get-govt-job%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecycle%20of%20poverty%3C%2Fa%3E%20force%20many%20farmers%20in%20Rajasthan%20to%20leave%20their%20families%20and%20seek%20better%20opportunities%20elsewhere.%20Their%20children%2C%20innocent%20victims%20of%20circumstance%2C%20are%20often%20forced%20to%20discontinue%20their%20education.%20Three%20young%20entrepreneurs%2C%20Satyam%20Bhandari%2C%20Rohit%20Negi%2C%20and%20Mohit%20Rana%2C%20were%20determined%20to%20change%20this%2C%20and%20through%20grit%20and%20hard%20work%2C%20they%20founded%20Foreka%2C%20a%20company%20that%20aimed%20to%20empower%20these%20farmers%20and%20uplift%20their%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20watched%20my%20mother%20struggle%20to%20become%20financially%20empowered%20so%20she%20could%20give%20me%20a%20better%20life%2C%20and%20that%20inspired%20me%20deeply.%20As%20I%20connected%20with%20farmers%20and%20tribals%2C%20I%20was%20reminded%20of%20her%20struggles.%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20do%20something%20for%20them%2C%20to%20ensure%20they%20too%20could%20have%20equal%20opportunities%2C%E2%80%9D%20Satyam%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Agastyamuni%2C%20a%20peaceful%20town%20cradled%20in%20the%20foothills%20of%20the%20Himalayas%2C%20Satyam%2C%20who%20lost%20his%20father%20at%20the%20age%20of%20four%2C%20had%20seen%20his%20mother%20work%20tireless