20farmers'%20livelihoods%20from%20unpredictable%20natural%20disasters.%20With%20increased%20funding%20and%20tech%20innovations%2C%20this%20scheme%20aims%20to%20provide%20financial%20stability%20and%20foster%20agricultural%20growth.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Mervin%20Preethi%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F394815%2Fcrop-insurance-schemes-india-2025-benefits-availability-pmfby-farmers%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Assam%20Farmer%E2%80%99s%20Daring%20Farming%20Methods%20Pushed%20Him%20From%20Daily%20Wage%20Worker%20to%20Padma%20Shri%20Winner%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EImagine%20a%20childhood%20where%20the%20jungle%20was%20your%20playground%2C%20a%20world%20of%20endless%20wonder%20and%20danger.%20A%20world%20where%20farming%20was%20a%20distant%20dream%2C%20and%20survival%20depended%20on%20what%20the%20forest%20provided.%20This%20was%20the%20reality%20for%20young%20Sarbeswar%20Basumatary%2C%20growing%20up%20in%20the%20remote%20reaches%20of%20Chirang%20district%2C%20Assam.%20Today%2C%20at%2062%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20a%20survivor%2C%20but%20a%20trailblazer%2C%20earning%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20for%20his%20revolutionary%20work%20in%20agriculture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20eight%20siblings%20%E2%80%94%20five%20brothers%20and%20three%20sisters%20%E2%80%94%20life%20in%20Panbari%2C%20in%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Chirang%20district%2C%20was%20difficult%20for%20Sarbeswar.%20His%20parents%2C%20who%20worked%20as%20labourers%20on%20construction%20sites%20and%20at%20landowners%E2%80%99%20homes%2C%20did%20their%20best%20to%20care%20for%20their%20children%2C%20but%20resources%20were%20scarce.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20days%20when%20we%20got%20lucky%2C%20they%20would%20find%20some%20work%2C%20but%20otherwise%2C%20we%20had%20to%20rely%20on%20the%20forest%20and%20the%20goodwill%20of%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sarbeswar%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3